{"tid":1403943,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[極重要提醒] 遊撃戰只可以對準親支目標，唔可以影響市民","createTime":"2019-08-04T01:15:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T01:26:49.000Z","uid":267881,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b7e5a45e299e0807803299655f1a37a5e2222850","tid":1403943,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T01:15:05.000Z","msg":"逰撃狗署狗宿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n傍晚遊擊紅隧然後即閃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n午夜再遊擊紅隧減輕對市民影響<br />\n<br />\n油尖旺佔馬路都係遊行後遺已經有預警<br />\n<br />\n85三罷都係有預警下搞交通<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n影響市民可免則免<br />\n最緊要有預警、短時間、設時限<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好遊擊到無辜市民<br />\n有好多人真係一家人出黎食個飯<br />\n或者趕住睇醫生、湊仔<br />\n留返俾班狗搞佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1107a73e8c1f095850e0901f75a4e1ef2664289","tid":1403943,"uid":262035,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T01:20:33.000Z","msg":"最重要係有預警同hit n run <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n前者一向都做得唔錯<br />\n後者要再進步"},{"pid":"872308528b8a9826ca603672148cdd37ba58bc0e","tid":1403943,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1107a73e8c1f095850e0901f75a4e1ef2664289","tid":1403943,"uid":262035,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T01:20:33.000Z","msg":"最重要係有預警同hit n run <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n前者一向都做得唔錯<br />\n後者要再進步"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T01:26:49.000Z","msg":"冇預警遊撃係要黎對準敵人，唔係市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果行動會影響市民日常就一定要預警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要分得好清楚"}]}